.TH SVLANG 1 "2026-02-15" "Daniel Nylander" "svlang Manual"
.SH NAME
svlang - Swedish NLP toolkit for translators
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B svlang
.RI [ OPTIONS ]
.I COMMAND
.RI [ ARGS ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
\fBsvlang\fR is a Swedish NLP toolkit for translators. It detects anglicisms (svengelska), checks translation consistency across PO/TS files, splits compound words, calculates LIX readability index, and provides Swedish-English dictionary lookups via Folkets lexikon.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.BR \-V ", " \-\-version
Show version number and exit.
.TP
.B \-\-about
Show application info and exit.
.SH COMMANDS
.TP
.BR svengelska " (alias: " sv ")"
Find anglicisms in Swedish text.
.RS
.TP
.BR \-t ", " \-\-text " " \fITEXT\fR
Text to check.
.TP
.BR \-f ", " \-\-file " " \fIFILE\fR
File to check.
.RE
.TP
.BR consistency " (alias: " con ")"
Check translation consistency across .po or .ts files.
.RS
.TP
.I FILES
One or more .po or .ts files.
.TP
.BR \-i ", " \-\-ignore\-case
Ignore case when comparing.
.RE
.TP
.BR compound " (alias: " split ")"
Split Swedish compound words.
.RS
.TP
.I WORDS
Words to split.
.RE
.TP
.B lix
Calculate LIX readability index.
.RS
.TP
.BR \-t ", " \-\-text " " \fITEXT\fR
Text to analyze.
.TP
.BR \-f ", " \-\-file " " \fIFILE\fR
File to analyze.
.RE
.TP
.BR lookup " (alias: " ord ")"
Look up Swedish-English translations (Folkets lexikon).
.RS
.TP
.I WORD
Word to look up.
.TP
.BR \-r ", " \-\-reverse
Search English to Swedish.
.TP
.BR \-s ", " \-\-search
Search by prefix.
.TP
.BR \-n ", " \-\-limit " " \fIN\fR
Maximum results (default: 20).
.RE
.SH EXAMPLES
.nf
svlang svengelska -t "Vi beh√∂ver implementera en ny approach"
svlang consistency file1.po file2.po
svlang compound "kontorsstol" "skrivbordslampa"
svlang lix -f document.txt
svlang lookup hund
.fi
.SH FILES
.TP
.I ~/.config/svlang/
Configuration files.
.TP
.I ~/.cache/svlang/
Cached data.
